name: Daroid sync lead
author: David Filskov
comment:
This sound is based on the lead from the song "Sandstrom" by Darude.

Try pitchbend for changing the texture.

If you intend to sample it use note F3, A#3 and D#4 - these are particularly rough and nice :)

name: Fatty-sequence
author: David Filskov
comment:
I have timed the envelope to the arpeggio, so if you follow the rythm when you add notes
to an arpeggio chord, you can make som quite interesting sequences.

You must use 2 or 4 notes to match the rythm.
